# Todo API Server built with Node, Mongo and Graphql

This repo contains Authenticate GraphQL Queries With JsonWebTokens(JWT) in Orm-NodeJS environment using:
- Node
- Mongo
- ✨Graphql ✨

## Getting Started

- Clone the repo. Switch to the repo downloaded.
- Install dependencies with `npm install`
- Run `npm install -g nodemon` to install Nodemon Globally.
- Run `npm start` to run the NodeJS Server.


## Database Setup

Download and isntall MogoDB. Make sure that the database is running at `127.0.0.1:27017`
